# prime-faster

## Description

This is a small program that finds all the prime numbers up to a given number faster than the naive algorithm.

## Install

```bash
$ pip install prime-faster
```

## Usage

```python
import primefaster

print(primefaster.is_prime(7))
# True
print(primefaster.get_prime(10))
# [2, 3, 5, 7]
```
